'''圣路茂狄主教座堂'''（{{lang-nl|Sint-Romboutskathedraal}}）是[[天主教梅赫伦-布鲁塞尔总教区|天主教梅赫伦-布鲁塞尔总教区]]的[[主教座堂|主教座堂]]，位于比利时[[梅赫伦|梅赫伦]]。本堂主保圣路茂狄是一位[[传教士|传教士]]和[[殉道者|殉道者]]，曾在附近建立[[修道院|修道院]]。<ref
 name=DE-HRum>{{Cite web |url=http://dagelijksevangelie.org/main.php?language=NL&module=saintfeast&localdate=20110701&id=890&fd=0 |title=H. Rumoldus van Mechelen (gedachtenis) |language=nl |publisher=Dagelijks Evangelie service ©Evangelizo.org, the Netherlands |accessdate=25 July 2011 |archive-date=2012-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328041940/http://dagelijksevangelie.org/main.php?language=NL&module=saintfeast&localdate=20110701&id=890&fd=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=DvdA-Fred>{{Cite web |url=http://www.heiligen.net/heiligen/07/17/07-17-0750-fredegand.php |title=Fredegand van Deurne |language=nl |author=Dries van den Akker s.j. |publisher=www.heiligen.net |date=10 August 2010 |accessdate=9 July 2011 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030629/http://www.heiligen.net/heiligen/07/17/07-17-0750-fredegand.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=CathOL>{{Cite web |url=http://www.catholic.org/saints/saint.php?saint_id=4662 |title=St Rumbold |publisher=Catholic Online |year=2011 |accessdate=5 July 2011 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184753/http://www.catholic.org/saints/saint.php?saint_id=4662 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=SRAbbeyToCathedral-source>{{Cite web |url=http://inventaris.vioe.be/dibe/relict/74569 |title=Sint-Romboutskerk (ID: 74569) |work=De Inventaris van het Bouwkundig Erfgoed |language=nl |publisher=Vlaams Instituut voor het Onroerend Erfgoed ([http://www.vioe.be/ VIOE]) |accessdate=15 July 2011 }}{{Dead link}}</ref> 其遗体葬于堂内。该堂建于13世纪初，1312年祝圣，1559年升格为主教座堂。

[[Image:SkywalkSintRombouts.jpg|thumb]]
其钟楼高达97.28米，始终未能完成，为[[世界遗产|世界遗产]][[比利时和法国的钟楼|比利时和法国的钟楼]]的一部分<ref name=IL_WH>[ref. [http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/943/multiple=1&unique_number=1100 whc.unesco.org: ID 943 016 St. Rumbolds Tower] {{Wayback|url=http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/943/multiple%3D1%26unique_number%3D1100 |date=20200726191500 }}</ref>，每年吸引许多游客。曾经造访的名人包括[[路易十五|路易十五]]、[[拿破仑|拿破仑]]等人。<ref name=SRT-Tw>{{Cite web |url=http://sintromboutstoren.mechelen.be/nl/3609/content/9139/torenweetjes.html |title=Sint-Romboutstoren Mechelen — Torenweetjes |language=nl |publisher='Sint-Romboutstoren': Toerisme Mechelen/Torenbalie/Stedelijke Musea Mechelen, Mechelen |accessdate=25 July 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180318154302/http://sintromboutstoren.mechelen.be/nl/3609/content/9139/torenweetjes.html |archive-date=2018-03-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref group="Note" name="Fire-1687>The full moon of 27 January 1687 caused all the stir about the presumed tower fire, reported as a 'happy-ending tragedy'. According to an 1808 sale's list {{Cite web  |url=http://books.google.be/books?id=dFAVAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA310&lpg=PA310&dq=Bly-eyndend+Treur-spel+op+St.-Rombouts+Tooren+den+27&source=bl&ots=t2HQNxsUBN&sig=oy6joUjFLcWGDu7-oM00yDBpWLg&hl=en&sa=X&ei=jOOuUdDDMpL07AaZyIHABQ&ved=0CEcQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=Bly-eyndend%20Treur-spel%20op%20St.-Rombouts%20Tooren%20den%2027&f=false |title=item 4242 |work=Catalogue des livres de la bibliothèque de feu monsieur Gaspar-Joseph de Servais (in French) |publisher=List: Hanicq, 1808 (Original from the Bavarian State Library online by Google books, 2011) |quote=4242. Maan - suchtigen Brand - sticht of Mechelsche beroerte. Bly-eyndend Treur-spel op St.-Rombouts Tooren den 27 january 1687, in volle maen, in-8°. met platen. V. |accessdate=28 July 2011 }} (in outdated Dutch)</ref>

